{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In any case, the two children of the Birch family and myself crawled up into this attic space, which was only high enough to lie down but not sit up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the building was quite long, so we crawled all the way back to the back of the building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we began to hear the noises of the Germans running around and hauling people out and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The mother of the two friends was going to act as if she were in charge of the building and be sweeping the grounds or something, and she thought maybe that would help.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we knew that the surround-- the ghetto was surrounded by these special troops.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only one thing that was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was sweeping the grounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, and my mother wasn't going to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, she was just going to take her chances and probably be shipped off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she remembered that we were up there, and we didn't have anything to eat or drink.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't take anything with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ended up there three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could have been three months, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's really three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she filled up a-- a teapot, a regular kind of normal teapot, full of water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was carrying it across the yard to hand it to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we could see her, because there was-- the building was not very well made, and there was some cracks in the-- in the roof, so we could see.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as she was coming up, the guards broke into the yard and started yelling for those people to get out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was just about to hand us the teapot.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
